snippet.textDisplay: I know how it feels to lose someone you love. R.I.P. Becker. About two years ago my grandparents dog died. He was awesome, his name was Waldo’s and was my first friend when I was born. He was always there for me and saved me, my grandfather, and grandmother countless times. He was amazing and when we used to live near my grandparents, we had a black lab named Sasha. She wasn’t Waldo’s biological mother, but acted like it and she passed away when I was too young to remember her. She was still an awesome dog, and when Waldo’s passes away, I cried myself to sleep. I loved him but, he was having some health issues and well, it was time for him to join his mother, Sasha. Remember to stay safe, and that there is always another way. I love you all and I’m very sorry for your loss Brent. Remember that Becker lived a good life, and probably couldn’t be happier with anyone else, and that he’s playing and being in the background of other YouTube videos in heaven. Stay safe and awesome, love ya.
